Sentencas: Fe-Cr-Ni ternary systems are of fundamental importance for solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) applications.
Titulo: Phase equilibria of the Fe-Cr-Ni ternary systems and interfacial reactions in Fe-Cr alloys with Ni substrate

Sentencas: Fe-Cr alloys are commonly utilized materials as interconnect materials and yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ) doped with Ni is the common anode materials.
Titulo: Phase equilibria of the Fe-Cr-Ni ternary systems and interfacial reactions in Fe-Cr alloys with Ni substrate

Sentencas: In this study, isothermal sections of the Fe-Cr-Ni ternary system at 750 and 850 degrees C were experimentally determined.
Titulo: Phase equilibria of the Fe-Cr-Ni ternary systems and interfacial reactions in Fe-Cr alloys with Ni substrate

Sentencas: In addition, the interfacial reactions in several Fe-Cr alloys with Ni were investigated.
Titulo: Phase equilibria of the Fe-Cr-Ni ternary systems and interfacial reactions in Fe-Cr alloys with Ni substrate

Sentencas: No ternary intermetallic compounds (IMCs) can be found at 750 degrees C, and only one ternary IMC, (T phase, existed at 850 degrees C in the Fe-Cr-Ni ternary systems.
Titulo: Phase equilibria of the Fe-Cr-Ni ternary systems and interfacial reactions in Fe-Cr alloys with Ni substrate

Sentencas: In the Fe-16 wt%Cr and Fe-25 wt%Cr couples, layer-shape alpha and gamma phases, and the island-shape alpha' phase were formed on the Fe-Cr/Ni interface at 750 degrees C. As the reaction temperature rose to 850 degrees C, only the alpha' and gamma phases can be observed.
Titulo: Phase equilibria of the Fe-Cr-Ni ternary systems and interfacial reactions in Fe-Cr alloys with Ni substrate

Sentencas: In Fe-80 wt%Cr and Fe-94 wt%Cr couples, alpha' and gamma phases are formed on the Fe-Cr interface at both 750 and 850 degrees C.
Titulo: Phase equilibria of the Fe-Cr-Ni ternary systems and interfacial reactions in Fe-Cr alloys with Ni substrate

Sentencas: The thickness of all reaction couples increased with longer reaction time and less Cr content in Fe-Cr alloys.
Titulo: Phase equilibria of the Fe-Cr-Ni ternary systems and interfacial reactions in Fe-Cr alloys with Ni substrate

Sentencas: All the IMCs growth mechanism can be described by the parabolic law.
Titulo: Phase equilibria of the Fe-Cr-Ni ternary systems and interfacial reactions in Fe-Cr alloys with Ni substrate

Sentencas: The IMCs growth is diffusion controlled.
